videos.headline: Raina Perez drains a 3 to continue NC State's hot start
videos.description: NC State continues its hot shooting in the first quarter as Raina Perez drains a transition 3-pointer to extend the lead over UNC to 24-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Raina Perez drains a 3 to continue NC State's hot start) 2022/01/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Elissa Cunane's double-double leads NC State past UNC
videos.description: Elissa Cunane puts up 19 points and 13 rebounds as she helps elevate NC State to a 72-45 win over North Carolina.
